---

What this means in plain language:

  ALLOWED:
  - Use KStack to build and run your own online store
  - Deploy KStack for a single client or business
  - Modify KStack for your own use
  - Contribute to the KStack project

  NOT ALLOWED:
  - Run KStack as a hosted SaaS platform where third-party merchants
    sign up and pay you to host their stores (i.e. building a
    Shopify / hosted e-commerce platform competitor)
  - Offer KStack as a managed hosting service sold to others

  If you want to run a hosted multi-tenant platform, contact us for
  a commercial license: https://kstack.dev/licensing

